<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Backyard - High Converting Landing Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Resetting defaults */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 16px; /* Text size bada kiya hai */
        }

        /* ==================================================== */
        /* 1. HERO SECTION (BADA LAYOUT WITH BACKGROUND)       */
        /* ==================================================== */
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1434030216411-0b793f4b4173?q=80&w=1200') no-repeat center center/cover;
            min-height: 90vh; /* Height barhadi hai */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 100px 10%; /* Khula padding space */
            gap: 60px;
        }

        .hero-left-content {
            flex: 1.3;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .hero-brand {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #2ed573;
        }

        .hero-left-content h1 {
            font-size: 52px; /* Heading badi kar di */
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .hero-left-content p {
            font-size: 18px; /* Paragraph bada kiya */
            color: #e0e0e0;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-inline-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn-blue-outline {
            background-color: #00a8ff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-transparent-outline {
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            padding: 14px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Form Container Box */
        .hero-right-form {
            flex: 0.9;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 40px 35px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
        }

        .hero-right-form h3 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-right-form input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .hero-right-form .btn-submit-form {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .form-disclaimer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #ccc;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* ==================================================== */
        /* 2. SUB-NAVBAR STRIP                                  */
        /* ==================================================== */
        .sub-nav-strip {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 10%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eeeeee;
        }

        .strip-logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .strip-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .strip-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .strip-links a.active-link {
            color: #3498db;
        }

        /* ==================================================== */
        /* 3. MIDDLE SHOWCASE (WITH WORKSPACE IMAGES)           */
        /* ==================================================== */
        .mid-showcase-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 100px 10%;
            gap: 60px;
        }

        .mid-left-visual {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .mid-left-visual img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 550px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .mid-right-text {
            flex: 1;
        }

        /* Choti extra image paragraph ke upar */
        .mid-top-mini-img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            height: 140px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .mid-right-text h2 {
            font-size: 34px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .mid-right-text p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn-blue-rect {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #3498db;
            border: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* ==================================================== */
        /* 4. RECREATE IDEAS (BOTTOM MATRIX WITH STUDENT PIC)   */
        /* ==================================================== */
        .grid-intro-section {
            padding: 100px 10%;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fafafa;
        }

        .grid-intro-section h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .grid-intro-section .subtitle-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #777;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .features-grid-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 50px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Student Image Custom Design */
        .grid-left-person-img {
            flex: 0.9;
        }

        .grid-left-person-img img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 320px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .grid-right-cards {
            flex: 1.4;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .mini-feature-block {
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 20px);
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .block-icon-area {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #3498db;
        }

        .block-text-area h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .block-text-area p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ==================================================== */
        /* 5. RESPONSIVE MEDIA QUERIES                          */
        /* ==================================================== */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero-section, .mid-showcase-section, .features-grid-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .hero-left-content p, .mid-top-mini-img {
                margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
            }
            .hero-inline-btns {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .hero-right-form {
                margin: 30px auto 0 auto;
            }
            .mid-left-visual img, .grid-left-person-img img {
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            .sub-nav-strip {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .strip-links {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .mini-feature-block {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
            .hero-left-content h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Main Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-left-content">
            <div class="hero-brand">Backyard</div>
            <h1>Beautiful High Converting Landing Page</h1>
            <p>Backyard is a modern and customizable landing page template designed to increase conversion of your product. Backyard is flexible to suit any kind of business. Try now and join with our happy customers!</p>
            <div class="hero-inline-btns">
                <button class="btn-blue-outline">Features</button>
                <button class="btn-transparent-outline">Download</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side Form Box -->
        <div class="hero-right-form">
            <h3>Get Started</h3>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your name">
            <input type="email" placeholder="Email address">
            <button class="btn-submit-form">Subscribe</button>
            <p class="form-disclaimer">We will not share your email. Read privacy policy.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- White Navigation Link Strip -->
    <div class="sub-nav-strip">
        <div class="strip-logo">Backyard</div>
        <ul class="strip-links">
            <li><a href="#" class="active-link">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Download</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Pricing</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Reviews</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Center Apple Computer Showcase Section -->
    <section class="mid-showcase-section">
        <div class="mid-left-visual">
            <!-- Left side Desktop Screen Setup -->
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513542789411-b6a5d4f31634?q=80&w=600" alt="Apple Desktop Layout">
        </div>
        <div class="mid-right-text">
            <!-- Text ke upar wali extra workspace picture jo aapne kahi thi -->
            <img class="mid-top-mini-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?q=80&w=500" alt="Workspace Concept">
            
            <h2>Optimize performance through advanced targeting solutions</h2>
            <p>Good marketing makes the company look smart. Great marketing makes the customer feel smart. Never doubt a small group of thoughtful, committed people can change the world. Indeed, it is the only thing that ever has. The best way to predict the future is to create it.</p>
            <button class="btn-blue-rect">Learn More</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Recreate Ideas Bottom Grid Section -->
    <section class="grid-intro-section">
        <h2>Recreate your ideas and gain more success</h2>
        <p class="subtitle-text">Increase your user loyalty by maintaining mutual communication and nurturing your online community.</p>

        <div class="features-grid-container">
            <!-- Right side par simple student look photo -->
            <div class="grid-left-person-img">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?q=80&w=400" alt="Student High School Girl">
            </div>

            <!-- Features Grid Matrix Box -->
            <div class="grid-right-cards">
                <div class="mini-feature-block">
                    <div class="block-icon-area">📋</div>
                    <div class="block-text-area">
                        <h4>Marketing Strategy</h4>
                        <p>Good marketing makes the company look smart. Great marketing makes the customer feel smart.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-feature-block">
                    <div class="block-icon-area">📦</div>
                    <div class="block-text-area">
                        <h4>App Monetization</h4>
                        <p>Content builds relationships. Relationships are built on trust. Trust drives revenue.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-feature-block">
                    <div class="block-icon-area">🛒</div>
                    <div class="block-text-area">
                        <h4>Store Optimization</h4>
                        <p>Never doubt a small group of thoughtful committed people can change the world.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-feature-block">
                    <div class="block-icon-area">👥</div>
                    <div class="block-text-area">
                        <h4>User Management</h4>
                        <p>Instead of using technology to automate processes, think about using technology to enhance human interaction.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
